GC-FID based FAs abundances in sunflower and rapeseed are in good agreement with those obtained in previous investigations (
 Alpaslan & Gündüz, 2000; 
 Pleite, Martínez-Force & Garcés, 2006; 
 Demurin & Borisenko, 2011; 
 Bocianowski, Mikołajczyk & Bartkowiak-Broda, 2012; 
 Sharafi et al., 2015).
